com.moblima.project.controller

Class CineplexManager

  • Object
    • Manager
      • CineplexManager

  • public class CineplexManager
extends Manager
    The manager class to manage the storage of all the models. All the model data is held inside corresponding ArrayLists. Any updates on the data is done on the ArrayLists here and files both.
